<head>
  <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/uikit@3.4.2/dist/css/uikit.min.css"
  />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{userData.theme}}.css">
  <title> {{userData.username}} </title>
  <style>
    
    body {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .container1 {
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .container2 {
      padding-top: 100px;
      padding-bottom: 200px;
    }

    .intro {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .userImg {
      border-radius: 100px;
    }

    .aboutme {
      width: 60%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      margin-bottom: 100px;
    }

    .aboutme > h2 {
      font-size: 60px;
    }

    .projects {
      width: 60%;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .projects > h2 {
      font-size: 60px;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .uk-accordion-title{
      color: #333;
      font-size: 32px;
    }
    .uk-accordion-title:hover{
      color: #333;
    }
    .uk-accordion-title:focus{
      color: #333;
    }

  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container1">
    <div class="intro uk-position-center">
      <img
        class="userImg"
        src="https://via.placeholder.com/200"
        alt="User Image"
      />
      <h1>Hi Im {{ userData.username }}</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container2">
    <div class="aboutme">
      <hr>
      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <p>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Harum quasi eveniet non nulla fugit. Unde, quaerat! Molestias ea vitae quos repellendus a maxime vero, commodi unde placeat tempora incidunt amet. Unde dicta ipsum aliquid quis laboriosam nemo alias accusamus cumque, consectetur velit mollitia et hic quas modi a fugit, sunt cum qui praesentium autem consequuntur facere. Natus blanditiis non doloremque omnis nostrum quos saepe, cumque placeat tempora laudantium eum provident temporibus adipisci! Optio, vel, consequuntur est porro excepturi deleniti eius ipsum beatae repellat magni quidem velit fuga doloribus nihil minus laboriosam consequatur? Voluptatibus, labore, soluta fugiat, mollitia aliquid quam enim alias velit temporibus facere porro! Neque accusamus totam consequuntur non quo consequatur minima impedit deserunt error, nam fuga vero repellendus eos magnam iste dolores atque! Voluptate id pariatur et dolores reprehenderit, beatae eos odit ab aut veniam inventore rem quia incidunt dicta impedit expedita earum eaque. Pariatur eaque laboriosam aperiam?
      </p>
    </div>

    <div  class="projects">
      <hr>
      <h2>Projects</h2>
      <ul uk-accordion>

        {{#each Repos}}
          <li>
            <a class="uk-accordion-title" href="#">{{name}}</a>
            <div class="uk-accordion-content">
              {{#if description}}
                <p>{{description}}</p>
              {{/if}}
              <a class="uk-button uk-button-default" href=" {{ repoUrl }} ">Github Repo</a>
            </div>
          </li>
        {{/each}}
      
      </ul>
    <div>
  </div>

  <!-- UIkit JS -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/uikit@3.4.2/dist/js/uikit.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/uikit@3.4.2/dist/js/uikit-icons.min.js"></script>
</body>
